{
  "id": 6552486106234880,
  "name": "Deprecate and Remove Protected Audience",
  "summary": "The Protected Audience API provides a method of interest-group advertising without third-party cookies or user tracking across sites.\n\nFollowing Chrome's announcement that the current approach to third-party cookies will be maintained, we are now planning to deprecate and remove the Protected Audience API (along with certain other Privacy Sandbox APIs, as outlined on the Privacy Sandbox feature status page).",
